 <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">Starting a charging accessories brand? One of the most critical decisions you'll face is choosing between <strong>OEM</strong> (Original Equipment Manufacturing, you provide the design, the factory builds it) and <strong>ODM</strong> (Original Design Manufacturing, the factory provides ready-made designs you brand as your own). This decision impacts your product quality, margins, time-to-market, and long-term competitive advantage.</p>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">With over a decade of experience as a <a href="/about" class="text-brandBlue hover:text-brandOrange underline">certified manufacturer in Shenzhen</a>, we've helped hundreds of brands navigate this decision. This guide covers everything you need to know, from basic definitions to advanced negotiation strategies.</p>

