 <li>, Real case studies and negotiation tactics</li>
 </ul>
 </div>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">According to IBISWorld, the global electronics OEM/ODM market is estimated at $280 billion, with China-based manufacturers representing approximately 65% of total production capacity (IBISWorld, 2024).</p>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">According to a 2024 Alibaba supplier quality report, only 12% of electronics suppliers on B2B platforms pass comprehensive third-party factory audits. This makes independent verification a critical step before committing to any partner (Alibaba, 2024).</p>
