 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">8. How to Negotiate with Charger Factories: Pricing, MOQ &amp; Contracts</h2>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Strong negotiation skills can save thousands and establish productive long-term partnerships. Here are proven tactics from our decade of manufacturing experience.</p>

 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
