 <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase italic mb-6">Common Negotiation Mistakes to Avoid</h3>
 
 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
 <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl p-4">
 <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 mb-2"><svg class="icon-xmark mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 384 512">
 <path d="M55.1 73.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0s-12.5 32.8 0 45.3L147.2 256 9.9 393.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3s32.8 12.5 45.3 0L192.5 301.3 329.9 438.6c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0s12.5-32.8 0-45.3L237.8 256 375.1 118.6c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L192.5 210.7 55.1 73.4z" fill="currentColor"/>
 </svg>Don't Do This</h4>
 <ul class="text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-1">
 <li>, Demanding the lowest price immediately</li>
 <li>, Revealing your target budget upfront</li>
 <li>, Threatening to walk away without intention</li>
 <li>, Comparing factories against each other publicly</li>
 <li>, Negotiating after signing the contract</li>
 </ul>
 </div>
 
 <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-4">
 <h4 class="font-bold text-green-700 mb-2"><svg class="icon-check mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 448 512">
