 </svg>Do This Instead</h4>
 <ul class="text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-1">
 <li>, Build relationship before discussing price</li>
 <li>, Show genuine interest in partnership</li>
 <li>, Offer value (repeat orders, referrals)</li>
 <li>, Be transparent about concerns</li>
 <li>, Focus on win-win solutions</li>
 </ul>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
