 <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">9. How to Choose Between OEM, ODM, and Hybrid (Decision Framework)</h2>

 <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Use this structured approach to determine which manufacturing model fits your specific situation.</p>
 
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
 <div class="space-y-6">
 <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
 <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">1</div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What's your total budget for this project?</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Under $20K:</strong> ODM is your realistic option. <strong>$20K-$50K:</strong> Hybrid approach works well. <strong>$50K+:</strong> Full OEM becomes viable with significant product differentiation.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 
 <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
 <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">2</div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">How unique does your product need to be?</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Same function, better branding:</strong> ODM is sufficient. <strong>Unique features/technology:</strong> OEM required. <strong>Some differentiation, faster time:</strong> Hybrid is the answer.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 
 <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
 <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">3</div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What's your time-to-market requirement?</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Under 2 months:</strong> ODM only. <strong>2-4 months:</strong> ODM or Hybrid. <strong>4+ months:</strong> Any model works with proper planning.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 
 <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
 <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">4</div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">What's your order quantity?</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Under 500 units:</strong> ODM required. <strong>500-1,000 units:</strong> Hybrid possible. <strong>1,000+ units:</strong> OEM becomes cost-effective.</p>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
 <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">5</div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Do you have technical expertise?</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>No engineering team:</strong> ODM, actory handles all technical decisions. <strong>Some technical knowledge:</strong> Hybrid works. <strong>Full engineering capability:</strong> OEM gives you maximum control.</p>
 </div>
 </div>

 <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
 <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brandBlue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black shrink-0">6</div>
 <div>
 <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Is IP protection critical?</h4>
 <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Sharing base tech is acceptable:</strong> ODM. <strong>Need exclusive design:</strong> OEM with full IP protection. <strong>Some exclusive features:</strong> Hybrid with selective exclusivity.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>

